            <p class="{{descSize}}">
              Aramid
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base  text-red-700 font-bold">
            VS
          </p>
          <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <picture>
              <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}" data-src="{{'vsimg-3.png' | asset_url}}" alt="Aramid Fibre Benefits"
                class="block object-cover lazyload">
            </picture>
            <p class="{{descSize}}">
              Carbon Fibre
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="{{descSize}}">
          What’s more, carbon fibre is very definitely conductive, Aramid fibre do not conduct electricity. In other
          words, a carbon (karbon)
          phone case has interruption to your signals. While the Aramid phone cases have no interruptions at all.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full text-center"> 
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-color-white mb-6 font-bold">
          <span class="text-red-700 font-bold">03</span> Color
        </p>
        <div class="w-full mb-6 flex flex-row justify-evenly items-center">
