            <picture>
              <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}" data-src="{{'vsimg-5.png' | asset_url}}" alt="Aramid Fibre Benefits"
                class="block object-cover lazyload">
            </picture>
            <p class="{{descSize}}">
              Aramid
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base  text-red-700 font-bold">
            VS
          </p>
          <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <picture>
              <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}" data-src="{{'vsimg-6.png' | asset_url}}" alt="Aramid Fibre Benefits"
                class="block object-cover lazyload">
            </picture>
            <p class="{{descSize}}">
              Carbon Fibre
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="{{descSize}}">
          Aramid in its natural state is a light golden colour. It can be coloured and many wonderful hues are now
